  "update_count": 38,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nWhen an extension specifies a devtools_page entry, a message channel is used behind the scenes to provide the associated API functionality. The DevTools doesn't fully validate messages it receives in this way, allowing an extension to run code within the DevTools context"
